{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"msg_lg4sgij94i8d2fm0iejin","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"448367318","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/private/tmp/tokenwarden-bench/claude-code/2026-07-21T17-57-52-415Z/caveman-docs-from-code-1/bench-artifacts/cache-api.md","content":"# Cache API\n\n## createCache()\n\nCreates a new cache instance with an internal `Map` for key-value storage.\n\n**Signature:**\n\n```js\ncreateCache()\n```\n\n**Returns:** Cache object with `get`, `set`, `delete`, and `clear` methods.\n\n## Methods\n\n### get(key)\n\nRetrieves the value associated with the given key.\n\n- **Parameter:** `key` - Cache key to look up.\n- **Returns:** Value if found, `undefined` if not.\n\n### set(key, value)\n\nStores a value under the given key.\n\n- **Parameters:**\n  - `key` - Cache key.\n  - `value` - Value to store.\n- **Returns:** The stored value.\n\n### delete(key)\n\nRemoves the value associated with the given key.\n\n- **Parameter:** `key` - Cache key to delete.\n- **Returns:** `true` if key existed, `false` if not.\n\n### clear()\n\nRemoves all entries from the cache.\n"}}],"model":"qwen/qwen3.5-9b","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":6284,"output_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":6263},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"511401dd-4ff7-4522-9745-b9d863255ab4","uuid":"58bc7b9a-e952-4452-a881-5e3ba39ffc47","timestamp":"2026-07-21T20:50:50.236Z"}
